Package: CaseAirCross
Title: Case-Crossover Analysis for Air Pollution Health Effects
Version: 0.1.0
Description: |
  An R package for analyzing short-term health effects of air pollution 
  using case-crossover design. Supports spatial matching of pollution 
  data (NetCDF format) and automated statistical modeling.
